
Master:
curl -sfL https://get.k3s.io | sh -

get Token:
sudo cat /var/lib/rancher/k3s/server/node-token


Workers:
Change <Token> With the real Token
curl -sfL https://get.k3s.io | K3S_URL=https://172.24.4.101:6443 K3S_TOKEN=<Token> sh -

